<div class="title">I Play It Safe</div>
<div class="substance">Alcohol - Beer</div>
<div class="author">by <a href="/experiences/exp.cgi?A=Search&AuthorSearch=Iowa+Punker&Exact=1">Iowa Punker</a></div>


<div class="ts-citation">Citation:&nbsp;&nbsp; Iowa Punker. "I Play It Safe: An Experience with Alcohol - Beer (exp14204)". <u>Erowid.org</u>. Dec 27, 2006. erowid.org/exp/14204</div>

<br/>



